### 4. Content Pages (Week 2–4 — Biggest Long-Term Win)

Create dedicated pages for each file type. Each page targets a high-volume search term and embeds the tool. This is how you get consistent organic traffic for years.

Add these routes to your React app:

| Page | Target Keyword | Monthly Searches |
|---|---|---|
| `/json-validator` | json validator online | 110K |
| `/yaml-validator` | yaml validator | 40K |
| `/csv-validator` | csv validator online | 12K |
| `/json-formatter` | json formatter | 180K |
| `/sql-formatter` | sql formatter online | 25K |
| `/python-syntax-checker` | python syntax checker | 8K |

Each page needs:
- A unique `<title>` and `<meta description>`
- A short paragraph explaining what the validator does
- The tool embedded and pre-filtered to that file type
- A simple FAQ section (Google loves these for featured snippets)

